name: Venture Capital DAO
description: It's a free social experiment, the Venture Capital DAO exists to be rich, so we're doing a really fun campaign where our donations can be invested in any opportunity to make money, and of course we can fail. Our DAO may be able to live in this world forever, but it may also be short-lived. Don't worry, it's just a social experiment!
